This is me learning to write games. I've chosen to use Ruby because I know it well enough to avoid wasting time on the language, but eventually I'd like to learn about games in C++ too.

I'd love any pointers anyone can give me on game design or ruby best practices.

gem install gosu
ruby main.rb

Move the mouse to target, left click to shoot, wasd or arrow keys move your little man.

The zombies have a bit of a massive hit box - sorry about that.
